  "title": "ASAP!! Junior Sales & Marketing (Fresh Grads/ORD)",
  "description": "<p><em>We're a dynamic and creative sales and marketing team that's all about having a blast while driving results! We're looking for a fun-loving and ambitious indivuduals to join our team and help us spread the excitement!</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong></p>\n<p><em>unior Sales and Marketing - you'll be the sparkplug that helps us ignite our sales and marketing efforts. You'll assist our team with a range of tasks, from client-customer management and campaign pitch creation to sales support and events/roadshows planning. If you're a creative problem-solver with a passion for sales and marketing, we want to hear from you!</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>1. Client-Customer Management: Assist with analyzing performance, understanding customer's need and feedback to enhance effectiveness of the campaign.</p>\n<p>2. Sales Support: Assist the sales team with lead generation, data entry, and sales research.</p>\n<p>3. Marketing Campaigns: Assist with developing and implementing marketing campaigns through face-to-face interactions.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<p>1. Dynamic Work Environment: Join a team that's passionate about creativity, innovation, and always having a good time.</p>\n<p>2. Opportunities for Growth: Develop your skillsets and experience in sales and marketing.</p>\n<p>3. Collaborative Culture: Work with a talented team that's always willing to lend a hand.</p>",
